i-Donate looks at an enduring giving and sharing process. It combines simplicity with disruption. It seeks to change the giving behavior and process. i-Donate proprietary solution is unique in its ability for contextual communication, which is a form of dynamic intelligence.

It is a cloud-based solution allowing nonprofits to focus on their primary goal – attract, retain and engage with donors and volunteers and allows Donors easy and quick access to information, set your goals, personalize your giving, track and share your giving and volunteer opportunities.
